@startuml
skinparam monochrome true
skinparam packageStyle rectangle
skinparam shadowing false

title System Sequence Diagram (SSD) - Alternative One

autonumber

actor "Agent" as Agent
participant ":System" as System

activate Agent

        Agent -> System : ask to list purchase order
    activate System

        System --> Agent : displays list of purchases orders grouped by property from the oldest to the most recent one
    deactivate  System

        Agent -> System :select purchase order
    activate System

        System --> Agent :display the list of purchase orders sorted by the amount offered, the highest offer appear first.
    deactivate System

        Agent -> System : select purchase order
    activate System

        System --> Agent : displays option list (Accept or Reject)
    deactivate  System

        Agent -> System :select option (Accept or Reject)
    activate System

        System --> Agent : system send email to client.
    deactivate System


@enduml